title: Flight Simulator 2020 - POI's - USA -  Pomham Rocks Light
description:
In this video we will fly over Pomham Rocks Light. Pomham Rocks Light (also known as "Pomham Lighthouse") is a historic lighthouse in the Providence River about 200 yards (180 m) off the shoreline of the Riverside neighborhood of the city of East Providence, Rhode Island. It is the northernmost lighthouse in Narragansett Bay.
